casebody.data:
Abdullah MUHAMMAD
v.
Darrel VANNOY, Warden Louisiana State Penitentiary NO. 2018-KH-1047 Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 29, 2019

Denied. Applicant has previously exhausted his right to state collateral review and fails to show that any exception permits his successive filing. See State ex rel. Muhammad v. State, 16-1573 (La. 1/9/18), 232 So.3d 543 .
